## Install the runtime SDK

The generated client delegates transport, signing, and lifecycle to `tx3-sdk`:

```sh
pip install tx3-sdk
```

If you also need a local dev runtime, `trix devnet` exposes a TRP endpoint at `http://localhost:8164`.

